snippet.title: Dawn of the Tiberium Age v3.0 (AKA build 1.12) trailer
snippet.description:
Dawn of the Tiberium Age (DTA) is a total conversion mod for C&C Tiberian Sun, which completely changes it into Tiberian Dawn (the first Command & Conquer game) and Red Alert.

DTA comes with 2 game modes:
Classic mode (1) tries mimic the gameplay of Tiberian Dawn as accurately as possible, while Enhanced mode (2) adds many new features for the Tiberian Dawn factions and also gives you access to the Red Alert factions.
This means that you can for example play with Nod against Soviet or mix it up however you like.

http://www.moddb.com/mods/the-dawn-of-the-tiberium-age
